description:
So my radar is going off on Lansing.
He does have a girlfriend, but there is an inner fire there that seems to be interested in dudes. I could be wrong, but I think he is one of those guys that isn't too sure what he is into yet, and maybe the video work is a safe way to explore?
Having said that, he sure was nervous to start with. But clearly he got way into the Serviced video.
I edited out a bit of craziness (Available on the new
Shear Chaos
DVD as a Bonus "Director's Cut- aren't I sneaky!?) but this is one dang hot video as he puts his ass out there like a cat in heat and the dynamic tension is intense!
A blistering hot Serviced video!
(A "
Mega Directors' Cut
" is now available on the site. It includes what is on the Shear Chaos DVD, plus a bit more action.
title: Bryan & Lansing - Serviced
